      "acceptanceCriteria": "Ansys Mechanical release validation documentation and FDA in-house verification scripts on record; version-controlled simulation environment with audit trail.",
      "rationale": "All three modeling teams (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) operate under documented SQA plans. Ansys Mechanical 2022R2 is a commercially validated solver with published verification benchmarks. FDA in-house scripts are version-controlled in a Git repository with tagged releases. Achieved level 3 exceeds the required level 2 for a Medium-risk COU."
