      "acceptanceCriteria": "Manufacturer-supplied benchmark suite reproduces analytical beam-bending solutions within 0.5% for the relevant load cases.",
      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical passes the NAFEMS benchmark suite for linear and nonlinear structural problems. Supplementary verification against Euler-Bernoulli beam theory for a simplified single-rod geometry confirmed < 0.3% discrepancy. Required and achieved levels are both 2, satisfying the acceptance criterion."
