      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Simulation setup reviewed by an independent analyst; checklist-based peer review completed prior to submission.",
      "rationale": "A second analyst independently reconstructed boundary conditions and material assignments from the simulation input deck and confirmed agreement with the documented setup. A formal peer-review checklist covering 22 items was completed with no unresolved findings. Use error controls meet the required level 2."
