      "rationale": "Construct stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm displacement are the three QoIs specified in the COU and are the standard ASTM F1717 endpoints used by FDA to evaluate pedicle screw construct performance. These quantities are directly linked to the risk of screw fracture and revision surgery cited in the decision consequence. Relevance is high and achieves level 3."
